230Ôćĺ\section{Seed Triples: The $(0, a, b)$ Structure}
231Ôćĺ\label{sec:seeds}
232Ôćĺ%======================================================================
233Ôćĺ
234Ôćĺ\subsection{Analytical condition}
235Ôćĺ
236ÔćĺFor a triple $(0, \zch_a, \zch_b)$ with one massless member, the 
237ÔćĺKoide ratio becomes:
238Ôćĺ\begin{equation}
239ÔćĺQ = \frac{\zch_a^2 + \zch_b^2}{(\zch_a + \zch_b)^2}\,.

